<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About PRISM Hospitality</title>
  <link
    href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
    crossorigin="anonymous"
  />
  <style>
    /* Ensure the content covers the full screen */
    html, body {
      height: 100%;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    }

    .about-prism {
      background-color: #f9f9f9; /* Light background color */
      padding: 30px; /* Adjust padding for better spacing */
      border-radius: 15px; /* Softer corners */
      box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* More pronounced shadow */
      margin: 30px 100px; /* Adjust top and bottom margin */
      width: 220px; /* This will make the container 1300 times the width of the viewport */
      height: auto; /* Adjust height based on content */
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-start; /* Align content to top */
    }

    /* Heading styling */
    .about-prism h3 {
      color: #921d21; /* Primary color */
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.5rem; /* Suitable heading size */
    }

    /* Paragraph styling */
    .about-prism p {
      color: #333; /* Dark text for better readability */
      font-size: 1.1rem; /* Standard font size */
      line-height: 1.7; /* Increased line height */
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: justify; /* Justified text for professional appearance */
    }

    /* Highlight key statistics */
    .about-prism span {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #921d21; /* Highlighted text color */
    }

    /* List styling */
    .about-prism ul {
      list-style-type: disc;
      margin-left: 40px;
      padding-left: 10px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    /* For very large screens (wide desktop) */
    @media (min-width: 900px) {
      .about-prism {
        width: 1300px; /* Same extreme width for large screens */
      }
      .about-prism h3 {
        font-size: 3rem; /* Larger heading for wide screens */
      }
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="about-prism">
    <h3>About PRISM Hospitality</h3>
    <p>
      We are a leading hospitality service provider with over <span>18+ years</span> of experience. Our commitment is to deliver sophistication and personalized service to our valued guests, combining impeccable cuisine with flawless service. With <span>5000+ events</span> organized and <span>150+ corporate clients</span> served, we take pride in our team of <span>1500+ professionals</span>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Across Telangana and Andhra Pradesh, we cater to <span>80,000 individuals daily</span>, including <span>20+ IT MNCs</span> with <span>8000 to 10,000 employees</span>. Additionally, we serve:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>19 international schools</li>
      <li>6 engineering colleges</li>
      <li>Hospitals, pharma companies, and public sector institutions</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Our extensive industry knowledge since 2005 empowers us to provide exquisite cuisine and dedicated service at every event. We continually strive for excellence through industry engagement and membership in culinary associations.
    </p>
    <p>
      Prism Hospitality's Central Kitchen offers comprehensive corporate food services, from unique working lunch boxes to customizable catering for gatherings of <span>50 to 2000+</span>. Our state-of-the-art kitchen, spanning over <span>6000 sq. ft.</span>, ensures fresh, hygienic, and competitively priced meals delivered promptly.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our tailor-made menus boast <span>300+ dishes</span>, prepared by trained chefs using high-quality ingredients. With attentive service and attractive presentation, we create successful and delectable events for gatherings of <span>25 to 10,000 guests</span>.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
